<h2>Names in the Economy (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>Onomastics goes business. Role and relevance of brand, company and other names in economic contexts </h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1745'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
